├─────────────────────┼────────────────────┼────────────────────┤
│  Use when...         │  Permissions are   │  Access depends on │
│                      │  static and based  │  resource state,   │
│                      │  on job function   │  ownership, time,  │
│                      │                    │  or context        │
├─────────────────────┼────────────────────┼────────────────────┤
│  Example             │  "Admins can       │  "Users can edit   │
│                      │  manage users"     │  their own posts   │
│                      │                    │  if draft"         │
├─────────────────────┼────────────────────┼────────────────────┤
│  Best for            │  Internal tools,   │  Multi-tenant SaaS,│
│                      │  CMS, most CRUD    │  healthcare,       │
│                      │  apps              │  finance           │
└─────────────────────┴────────────────────┴────────────────────┘
